    <p class="lead">The best AeroPress coffee method for most people is still the classic standard brew. It is clean, forgiving, and easy to repeat before your brain is fully online.</p>
    <p>That said, “best” changes fast once you know what kind of cup you actually want. Some methods make a brighter, cleaner mug. Some lean thicker and punchier. Some are just easier when you are brewing in a hotel room with one outlet and a suspicious kettle. The trick is not finding the fanciest recipe. It is finding the method you will happily use again tomorrow.</p>
